{"tid":1567031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"死線同升級 = 唱歌跳舞嗌口號拉人鏈？羞家！","createTime":"2019-09-14T01:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T10:21:04.000Z","uid":241151,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4e0218f6f928f67c74dd0704a9d1c9e275e17b53","tid":1567031,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:15:01.000Z","msg":"我去neway抗爭唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好問我點點點，我支持落場踢波，唔係黎唱歌<br />\n<br />\n咁你實問，你落場踢波啦笨，仲唔去踢？ 喂！我講句真話踢爆泛民既奸計都要俾泛民左膠屈係五毛啦，你地班鬼搞到個氣氛膠化晒又唔肯停止阻人衝同滅火，仲咁厚面皮叫人出黎？你地真係真心想香港市民係呢場抗爭贏既，就主動鼓吹返個勇武氣氛出黎啦，但係你地又自私又驚呀，驚死香港真係行岩路肯真正勇武，搞到你班泛民和理非左膠跟唔到呢個節奏隨時露低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646c070adc791422ddc0e7aee25422e4d0e187b0","tid":1567031,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:20:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請善用起底功能</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fc1085e2cd8cea82b18d1563e460b187a517585f","tid":1567031,"uid":241151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"646c070adc791422ddc0e7aee25422e4d0e187b0","tid":1567031,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:20:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請善用起底功能</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:25:41.000Z","msg":"我用圖答你呢隻賤人，好彩連登仲有有良心既人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iajeVC1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiajeVC1.png&h=2059eb49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94b8ae2869bf7d588b0738c89e0f51ceec164183","tid":1567031,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid